title: Kampanjen ”Ring Ryssland” siktar på 40 miljoner samtal
cleaned_sentences: A campaign called in English is called "Call Russia", with access to 40 million telephone numbers in Russia, has been launched in Lithuania.
The purpose is to inform Russian residents as much as possible about the war in Ukraine.
The campaign wants to take help from Russian -speaking people in the outside world to break through the Russian propaganda and censorship.
